ąIn loving memory of Claude Attwood
1916 2005
is spot by the river was one of Claude's favourite places,
where he would often sit and chat to passers by.
A proud and loving husband, father, grandfather and brother
sadly missed by all.

Gladys Mary Attwood (Nana)
1917-2012
Back with her beloved Claudie
And always in our hearts"┘
